            "notes": "The key concept of this deck is to control the game through counterspells, card draw, and tempo plays while using Aang, Swift Savior as the commander to maintain pressure on the opponent and close out the game quickly. The deck includes a variety of interaction spells like Counterspell, Force of Negation, and Mana Leak to disrupt the opponent's game plan, along with cards like Spell Queller and Palace Jailer to exile threats from the board. The inclusion of cards like Baleful Strix and Hullbreacher provides additional value and disruptive elements. By controlling the game state and leveraging Aang's abilities, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent and secure a victory through a mix of aggressive plays and strategic decision-making."
